data.description: Porch front house that is in very good condition, will make an nice home or rental. First floor: Living area, walk in to the dining area and eat in kitchen. Second floor: 3 bedroom and modern bath. Basement is finished with laundry room and walk out to rear with one car garage. This is an estate property and is sold as is, however, is in very good condition and you can move right in for a below market price. New carpet and all systems are in good working condition. All offers will be presented, ez to show and see.
